# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# APG Marketing Analytics Plugin — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# Then follow SETUP.md for step-by-step instructions on getting each credential.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── Meta Marketing API ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Required for: Pulling ad campaign data (campaigns, ad sets, ads, insights)
#
# How to get this token:
#   1. Go to https://developers.facebook.com/tools/explorer/
#   2. Select your app (or create one at https://developers.facebook.com/apps/)
#   3. Click "Add a Permission" and select: ads_read, read_insights
#   4. Click "Generate Access Token"
#   5. Copy the token below
#
# Note: Tokens from the Explorer tool are SHORT-LIVED (~1-2 hours).
#       You'll need to regenerate when it expires.
#
META_ACCESS_TOKEN=

# ─── Google Analytics 4 (Optional) ───────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Required for: Pulling landing page analytics and conversion data
#
# You need TWO things:
#   1. A GA4 Property ID (numeric, found in GA4 Admin → Property Settings)
#   2. A service account JSON key with Viewer access to the property
#
# GA4_PROPERTY_ID is for your primary landing page (e.g., go.yourdomain.com)
# GA4_PROPERTY_ID_HOME is for your main website (optional, e.g., yourdomain.com)
#
# How to set up the service account:
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com
#   2. Create or select a project
#   3. Enable "Google Analytics Data API" in API Library
#   4. Go to IAM & Admin → Service Accounts → Create Service Account
#   5. Download the JSON key file
#   6. Place the JSON file in this plugin directory
#   7. Go to GA4 → Admin → Property Access Management
#   8. Add the service account email as Viewer
#
# See SETUP.md for detailed instructions.
#
GA4_PROPERTY_ID=
GA4_PROPERTY_ID_HOME=
GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=ga4-service-account.json

# ─── Apify (Competitor Intelligence) ─────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Required for: Scraping competitor ads from Meta Ad Library
#
# How to get this token:
#   1. Sign up at https://apify.com
#   2. Go to https://console.apify.com/account/integrations
#   3. Copy your Personal API Token
#
APIFY_API_TOKEN=

# ─── fal.ai (Video Generation) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Required for: Generating video ad creatives via Kling 3.0 / Veo 3.1
#
# How to get this key:
#   1. Sign up at https://fal.ai
#   2. Go to https://fal.ai/dashboard/keys
#   3. Create a new API key
#
FAL_API_KEY=
